# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:13
translate portuguese whitney16_50df7566:

    # "My phone buzzes in my pocket. Whitney's calling."
    "O meu telemóvel vibra no bolso. É a Whitney a ligar."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:17
translate portuguese whitney16_0b8efa0c:

    # pc "Hey, Whitney."
    pc "Olá, Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:19
translate portuguese whitney16_c6ee1dad:

    # wt "Could you come over to the lab? I have something to show you."
    wt "Podes vir ao laboratório? Tenho uma coisa para te mostrar."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:20
translate portuguese whitney16_61f77a4c:

    # pc "Sure."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:21
translate portuguese whitney16_a1cf6718:

    # wt "Good. See you soon."
    wt "Ótimo. Até já."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:22
translate portuguese whitney16_897088bb:

    # "She hangs up before I can say anything else. Guess I better head over to the lab."
    "Ela desliga antes de eu conseguir dizer mais alguma coisa. Acho que é melhor ir ao laboratório."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:25
translate portuguese whitney16_fa8b8cd1:

    # "A few minutes later, I walk into the lab, where she's busy at her computer."
    "Alguns minutos depois, entro no laboratório, onde ela está ocupada ao computador."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:26
translate portuguese whitney16_4d683f87:

    # wt "Oh, [pcname]. Good. Follow me."
    wt "Oh, [pcname]. Ótimo. Segue-me."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:29
translate portuguese whitney16_1e926628:

    # wt "I have finished the new hoop."
    wt "Acabei o novo brinco."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:30
translate portuguese whitney16_22c83dc1:

    # pc "It's much bigger than the last one."
    pc "É muito maior do que o anterior."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:31
translate portuguese whitney16_984bce26:

    # wt "Yes, it's true. In this case, size does matter."
    wt "Sim, é verdade. Neste caso, o tamanho importa."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:32
translate portuguese whitney16_650aeb95:

    # wt "I've designed the new hoop so that it will not only transport you to the exact world that your father went to, but it will also bring you back."
    wt "Concebi o novo aro para que não só te transporte para o mundo exato para onde o teu pai foi, mas também te traga de volta."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:33
translate portuguese whitney16_d0034e37:

    # wt "It is synced with your DNA profile. When you go through it, you will be tethered to it. I can bring you back from here."
    wt "Está sincronizado com o teu perfil de ADN. Quando o atravessares, ficarás ligado a ele. Posso trazer-te de volta a partir daqui."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:34
translate portuguese whitney16_5b38bd59:

    # wt "This is what we should have done with your father, if he had been more patient."
    wt "Era isto que devíamos ter feito com o teu pai, se ele tivesse sido mais paciente."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:37
translate portuguese whitney16_994924ab:

    # pc "So, it's ready to go?"
    pc "Então, está pronto a funcionar?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:38
translate portuguese whitney16_c60270d5:

    # wt "Not quite. We have to test it first."
    wt "Ainda não. Temos de o testar primeiro."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:39
translate portuguese whitney16_74dfd840:

    # pc "How do we do that?"
    pc "Como é que fazemos isso?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:42
translate portuguese whitney16_a54b5eec:

    # wt "This morning, before you got here, I sent a mouse through."
    wt "Esta manhã, antes de chegares, enviei um rato através dele."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:43
translate portuguese whitney16_c4971b1e:

    # pc "Wait, really? You sent a mouse into another universe?"
    pc "Espera, a sério? Enviaste um rato para outro universo?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:44
translate portuguese whitney16_6f0e0998:

    # wt "Yes. That's the easy part."
    wt "Sim. Essa é a parte fácil."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:45
translate portuguese whitney16_a992c7cf:

    # wt "Now though, I'm going to try to bring it back."
    wt "Agora, porém, vou tentar trazê-lo de volta."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:48
translate portuguese whitney16_91de8169:

    # "She presses a series of buttons on her watch and the hoop glows to life."
    "Ela pressiona uma série de botões no relógio e o aro ganha vida, brilhando."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:49
translate portuguese whitney16_83bcc1d8:

    # "My ears pop as the air pressure in the room changes and there's a slight ringing sound."
    "Os meus ouvidos estalam à medida que a pressão do ar na sala muda e ouve-se um leve zumbido."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:52
translate portuguese whitney16_7d1c036c:

    # "Then the sound dissipates and there is something lying on the platform near the hoop."
    "Depois, o som dissipa-se e há algo deitado na plataforma perto do aro."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:53
translate portuguese whitney16_daaa84a9:

    # pc "What the fuck is that?"
    pc "Que raio é aquilo?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:54
translate portuguese whitney16_e0330bbf:

    # wt "That... is the mouse."
    wt "Isso... é o rato."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:57
translate portuguese whitney16_2681ebe7:

    # wt "It seems there is some more testing that must be done."
    wt "Parece que há mais alguns testes que têm de ser feitos."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:58
translate portuguese whitney16_4492000b:

    # pc "Yeah, I'd say so!"
    pc "Pois, diria que sim!"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:59
translate portuguese whitney16_2551790c:

    # wt "I'll figure it out. We're close."
    wt "Vou descobrir. Estamos perto."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:62
translate portuguese whitney16_004ba629:

    # wt "This is the last little bit to solve, though."
    wt "Mas isto é a última parte que falta resolver."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:63
translate portuguese whitney16_9edb80ec:

    # wt "The hoop is built. It's ready."
    wt "O aro está construído. Está pronto."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:64
translate portuguese whitney16_b679ea6d:

    # wt "It's just finding out how to do this in a way that we can bring you back in one piece."
    wt "É só descobrir como fazer isto de forma a que possamos trazer-te de volta inteiro."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:65
translate portuguese whitney16_19874614:

    # wt "I'll let you know as soon as I figure it out, okay?"
    wt "Aviso-te assim que descobrir, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:68
translate portuguese whitney16_8c9138ff:

    # pc "Okay. Thanks, Whitney."
    pc "Está bem. Obrigado, Whitney."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:69
translate portuguese whitney16_d39969f2:

    # wt "You're welcome. Sorry for calling you out here for nothing. I really thought that this would be successful."
    wt "De nada. Desculpa ter-te chamado aqui para nada. Eu realmente pensei que isto fosse dar certo."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:70
translate portuguese whitney16_e9a3252a:

    # wt "That is why we are patient though. That is why we test."
    wt "É por isso que somos pacientes. É por isso que fazemos testes."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:71
translate portuguese whitney16_4c58fa25:

    # wt "Back to work for me. I'll talk to you later."
    wt "Volto ao trabalho. Falo contigo mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:72
translate portuguese whitney16_0854e810:

    # pc "Okay, see ya later."
    pc "Está bem, até logo."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:75
translate portuguese whitney16_0ee8d1bf:

    # "I leave her lab, the image of that mouse in my mind."
    "Saio do laboratório dela, com a imagem daquele rato na minha mente."

# game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:76
translate portuguese whitney16_97666c57:

    # "Fuck, I hope Dad is okay."
    "Raios, espero que o pai esteja bem."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Whitney/whitney16.rpy:5
    old "A week after the jewelry store robbery, Whitney will call you on an afternoon on the weekend."
    new "Uma semana após o assalto à joalharia, a Whitney vai ligar-te numa tarde de fim de semana."

